{"tid":771880,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"柒！請689抖音說UGL","createTime":"2018-08-08T10:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T11:24:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4fffb62c9951e69ce441058a224fe1a64cf389","tid":771880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180808/20470989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F20470989&d=AjvRlTjlLkzCUhfqY%2B9749tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=25098cf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F20470989&h=d4efab4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180808/20470989</a><br />\n<br />\n柒！請689抖音說UGL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180808/large/1533635804_8956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180808%2Flarge%2F1533635804_8956.jpg&h=d8b3442e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n689被777擠落台後，越發「周轉」不靈，急於轉移視線，唔忌先撩者賤，四圍撥火，唔夠猛就出律師信去搶火。<br />\n<br />\n今次，FCC點樣回拖？發帖，請各方武林大會開talk，主題係辣到佢面青的UGL！港毒，唔講得，UGL？全城只有一個689鼻孔出煙，抖音說不！<br />\n<br />\nFCC三小時內必然收到律師信，但律師信只能唬嚇無人無物的小市民，叫立法會議員收聲都無力（淨得一個周乜頂自甘墮落隨狼起舞），更何況叫臥虎藏龍的外國記者會收皮？<br />\n<br />\n挑起記者條筋，外媒和港媒自動波埋位做嘢，肯定開talk講足柒日！UGL開壇，冇地方比得上FCC，689在fb打嘴炮天下無敵，發律師信當自己係差佬派牛肉乾。到當面對質，就縮窒過一條隔夜粉腸（網友形容）！這條公式，做了N次，當事人一再發、再發、再發律師信，「病發」頻繁但唔肯包膠，毫無疑問是對法律專業的淫褻不雅！<br />\n<br />\n689UGL五千萬，這組令人深感不安的密碼，屬於某人難逃的毒咒，但不是香港難以脫鉤的降頭。破解這種二級詛咒，欠的，極有可能就是關鍵那個7！借定唔借？告定唔告？全在阿柒。  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\nCY有心　CL無意 (尊子)"},{"pid":"0d9cb612feb7bc908fe661d46ec98820d5fdc819","tid":771880,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/192446_fd75af95b2a57b591442afcae2bb36ba.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F192446_fd75af95b2a57b591442afcae2bb36ba.gif&h=682358c4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}